description: Deletes a Device Defender audit suppression. Requires permission to access the DeleteAuditSuppression action.

parameters.name: checkName
parameters.description: An audit check name. Checks must be enabled for your account. (Use DescribeAccountAuditConfiguration to see the list of all checks, including those that are enabled or use UpdateAccountAuditConfiguration to select which checks are enabled.)
